Add option to close toast on click (#7)

Added the option to close the toast on click.
Its set to false by default.

Can be passed as as an option when creating a new toast,

nativeToast({
  message: 'wait wait!',
  closeOnClick: true
})

Add Result#sequence (#2)

Result#sequence would call the block on each item in the collection
in turn until either they have all been processed and returns Result.ok,
or one returned Result.error, in which case that one is returned.
